This livestream is now over. Watch a recording aboveJOHANNESBURG - Minister of Finance Malusi Gigaba has been meeting on Friday with CEOs who are part of the CEO Initiative.The minister and business leader Jabu Mabuza briefed the media after the meeting. The CEO Initiative was undertaken in 2015 at the request of President Jacob Zuma and Deputy President Cyril Ramaphosa in light of the investor crisis the country was facing, to try and stave off credit-ratings downgrades and transform the economy. eNCA